title: loadlib
description: A function from an imported library.

proc.description: The process where the library was loaded.

va.description: The base memory address where the library was loaded in the process.

loaded.description: The time the library was loaded.

unloaded.description: The time the library was unloaded.

file.description: The library file that was loaded.
